{"name":"write","arguments":{"path":"workspace/shadow-realm/chapter-002.md","content":"# Chapter 2: The Spreading

By morning, the shadows had spread beyond the Archive. They crawled along walls and whispered in voices that sounded like her own. The box was not a container — it was a key.
"}}

{"name":"write","arguments":{"path":"workspace/shadow-realm/chapter-003.md","content":"# Chapter 3: The Bargain

A figure emerged from the darkness. "Return what you took, or the shadow realm consumes your world." Mara clutched the box. "What do I get?" "A place in both worlds." The shadows receded.
